MAISON MARGIELA CLUB C SHOES
LEATHER SNEAKERS DESIGNED IN COLLABORATION WITH MAISON MARGIELA
The Maison's numerical logo and trompe-l'oeil house code from the early 90s unites with Reebok's Club C tennis shoe ‚Äì the 'C' short for 'Champion' ‚Äì since 1985. The familiar design receives the trompe-l'oeil treatment, constructed from a single piece of flat leather, the upper is printed with a scanned image of Reebok's original Club C shoe. The effect mimics every stitch, curve, and shadow of the original 3D surface, achieving a 2D optical illusion. They feature a lace closure, textile lining, and durable rubber outsole.

description:
Check out this dope vintage Cingular Wireless tee! They don't make these anymore, Cingular was bought out a decade ago!!!
This regular fit crewneck tee by Hanes Heavyweight is a men's size extra large XL. The heavyweight tee is 100% preshrunk cotton.
This white tee shirt has a small Cingular Wireless Mobile logo of the orange man at the left breast. Cingular Wireless is spelled out in blue font. On the back, there is a larger version of the Cingular graphic.
Really cool tee since Cingular has been out of business for a long time. Younger people may not even remember what Cingular was, but they were a telecom and cell phone service company in the 1990s nd 2000s that was acquired by T-Mobile (I believe, don't quote me). Fans of vintage technology, vintage phones, Y2K, dot com, cell phone history, telecom, mobile phones, legacy providers, etc will enjoy this cool vintage tee!
Tee is in great condition with no rips, holes, tears, or stains.

description:
With one of the most legendary takes on the classic biker leather jacket, Hedi outdid himself with this combination of luxurious hardware in multiple zippers and snap buttons situated wherever possible. The leather is obviously carefully selected 100% calf skin with a rigid surface not at all susceptible of permanent scratches like our otherwise beloved L01 lamb leather jacket that will look completely ruined after a night on the town.
üö®üö®üö®UPDATE 2023.01.23üö®üö®üö®
The cologne has now been processed and almost neutralized by Arm & Hammer baking soda balls and so the issue is practically non-existing now. Shout out to a fellow Grailor @yoitstommyguitar who tipped me to put the jacket in a huge vacuum sealer bag with baking soda balls and just leave it there for months. Now, the cologne is only a vague remembrance when getting close to the leather with your nose. A pleasant and underlying clean scent of Arm & Hammer has taken over, great success!!!!!
The hanger is now broken unfortunately, but I‚Äôll include it in the parcel anyway. The leather strings are included. Just didn‚Äôt take fitpics with them hooked on.
üö®üö®üö®EOMüö®üö®üö®
I bought this jacket from a cologne AFICIONADO and I mean capital letters for real. Told me he was a bit of a connaisseur when it comes to niche perfumes and that this jacket has been in the garment bag in his closet for years. Either way, when unboxing the parcel, a whiff of heavy Italian fragrance hit my nostrils but I thought it would rub off in time and kept it in my homeoffice to hang freely. This resulted in a headache and action was definitely needed. I placed the jacket on an other hanger than the branded one included and let it hang for weeks in our garage, sealed off the top with a plastic bag and put a bowl of vinegar right underneath to try and absorb the scent from the leather. This had a minimum effect, so I went ahead and sent it to the dry cleaner's which helped tremendously and a lot of the perfume is out now. But bear in mind that the scent is still present and somewhat heavy, tolerable for me at least in the sense that I won‚Äôt have to put on any eau de parfum when wearing the jacket.
Hence, as a disclaimer, know that you might want to work further with any local appliances available in your country. As far as I know, the stuff Denmark has to offer can't get me any closer to a completely scent-free leather jacket. I did have a correspondence with a fellow Grailor and we ended up debating whether baking soda could do the trick. Turns out I‚Äôm just too much of a pussy to make such an attempt.
Anyway, the overall condition is neat, no holes, no rips, no major scuffs or any of the likes. Some of the belt loops and rivets on the buckle have oxidised a bit (see photos) and this is all there is to say, really. The silverfish obviously came off in one side.
This piece is heavy duty and I'm not going to ship with Post Nord. UPS has proven to be far more reliable worldwide and the price for shipping is no more and no less than $80,-
No tags, but otherwise everything OG is included; Garment bag, two long leather strings and one short (unused, only applied before shooting the detail pic at the zipper for this listing), string bag, hanger.
Re-listing and aim to sell at this price.

The ring was presented in the legendary ad campaign for the Saint Laurent FW13 collection.
Grab this amazing piece from an iconic collection which is not only made from great materials and constructed very well - it is also crazy rare and very hard to find.
Comes with the original Saint Laurent leather pouch.

Product Description

description:
LAST DROP, NO OFFERS.
The now defunct Yeezy Gap Engineered by Balenciaga collaboration created history on January of 2022 when Ye (FKA Kanye West) while partnered with Gap, brought alongside the Creative Director of Balenciaga: Demna Gvasalia, to design multiple pieces for a collection.
The hoodie was unsurprisingly a focal point in the collaboration as hoodies have been dubbed by Ye to be ‚Äúarguably the most important piece of apparel of the last decade‚Äù.
With this collaboration, Ye & Demna created what is now known as the ‚ÄúYeezy Gap Balenciaga Logo Hoodie‚Äù. Heavier than your average hoodie, it‚Äôs Double Layered for thickness and warmth, features a unique raised neckline forming a cowl-like hood to protect your head, and has a small high quality rubberized ‚ÄúGAP‚Äù printed on the garment in the front on the neck to indicate . Very oversized which is not unusual or uncommon in Demna‚Äôs designs, this hoodie creates an interesting shape with the cropped construction through the elastic waist band and internal cuffs that hug to your body. While the rest of it flows with an oversized chest and arms creating a ‚Äúbat‚Äù like effect. You‚Äôll be sure to be the coziest person in the room.
Tagged sized Medium but can fit almost anyone as it is so oversized aside from the slight crop. Constructed in a 58% Cotton & 42% Polyester Shell and features a 100% Cotton T-shirt material like lining inside that separates from the shell.
Brand New in the very rare color of ‚ÄúDark Green‚Äù. You will never see these again as the partnership has officially ended and there are no longer any retailers selling this collection. Leaving the existing pieces in circulation to be the only ones left to tell the story.
My apologies but the sale will be United States only. Buyer accepts that there are no returns and the color of the garment is best to be determined by the stock photo in the first image of listing as lighting may alter the perception of the color in the photos taken by the seller.
Thank you so much.

description:
Brand: Vans x Imran Potato
Style: Knu-Skool VR3 LX
Size: 10 US
Color: Leopard Asphalt
Condition: Deadstock
Season: SS22
Thoughts: Chunky vans chunky vans.
Vault by Vans taps New Jersey born and raised designer, Imran Potato, for a six-piece footwear collection. Imran has built his creative identity by subverting fashion with humor in all that he does. Motivated to inspire others that nothing is impossible, Imran has found himself at the crossroads of disruption and design.


For his debut Vault by Vans collection, Imran helps to reissue the KNU SKOOL VR3 LX, a model that pays homage to the early ‚Äò90s skate-inspired footwear silhouette the brand first debuted in 1998 and later re-released via Vans Japan exclusively. For its latest iteration, Imran has taken the oversized DNA and further exaggerated its design specs to include all-over suede uppers with contrast stitching along with a quintessential 3D Sidestripe that protrudes from the quarter-panel.

The KNU SKOOL has been updated with an overstuffed tongue, thick cotton laces and a custom printed Potato waffle sole. Available in three colorways including classic Black, and two all-over cheetah prints available in asphalt/black and golden glow/Bombay brown.
To modernize the KNU SKOOL, the shoe‚Äôs suede panels are sourced from a top-rated LWG tannery for environmental responsibility. The silhouette is also a part of Vans VR3, representing the brands journey towards 100% regenerative, responsibly sourced renewable and recycled materials for the brands top four materials by 2030. The silhouette is also equipped with an EVA foam EcoCush‚Ñ¢ footbed derived partially from sugarcane and an EcoWaffle‚Ñ¢ rubber outsole that was obtained from sources that follow proven sustainable practices with the intention of reducing impacts on the planet.

description:
Back around 2010, the mature, more indulgent older brother of VANS Classics, VANS Vault, teamed up with American heritage label, Filson, to create a capsule collection of sneakers and a backpack that combines both VANS' skate-style and Filson's vintage sensibility. The collaboration consisted of a collaborative SK8-Hi LX in tonal brown canvas with brown leather accents with a special embroidered Filson tag sewn onto the leather and canvas insoles; a low-top 46 LX in the same colorway, and THIS ‚Äúspecial vintage-looking rucksack‚Äù in matching colorways. These days, it is not about securing the "it" shoes or sneakers or bag, but more about finding the "where did you get that" items. And, for fans of VANS, this collaboration definitely falls under that category.
Filson addicts know that you‚Äôre not likely to find this rare bag in such good condition anywhere. It took me years to find it and it served me well. But, it‚Äôs now time to pass it onto its next owner.
Aside for some basic wear-and-tear (which only adds to its character and is easily addressed), this bag is a flawless example of the collection. Filson bags get better with age; they earn a patina over time. This bag is in such great condition that you can still claim ownership over what it becomes.
FEATURES:
-15‚Äù Laptop sleeve (plus additional document sleeve) with snap closure.
-Fleece-padded shoulder straps and trim in standard Filson bridle leather
-outer back pocket
-two front pockets with snap closures
-large main interior pocket with waterproof zipper and ruck flap
-pen, pencil, pad and phone pockets in main compartment

Constructed with a low top, lace-up profile, this shoe also features sturdy, custom-designed suede uppers, metal eyelets, and signature rubber waffle outsoles.
